title: [Patreon Preview] Bay Of Pigs with Tommy Caprio
itunes:title: [Patreon Preview] Bay Of Pigs with Tommy Caprio
description:
This week, we have a good friend of the gang join us for the first time in a long time, Tommy Caprio! In this episode, Jim pitches a dating show to Tommy, talks about big ass Australian things, and shares another classic Australian song that'll probably haunt your dreams just like True Blue did.

Subscribe to our Patreon at patreon.com/IDKAT for ad free episodes, bonus episodes, and more exclusive perks! Tiers start at just $2!
